<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Pandit Assigned for Your Pooja</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #e8f5e9; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .otp-box { 
            background-color: #f1f8e9; padding: 15px; text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0;
            border: 2px dashed #4CAF50;
        }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Pandit Assigned for Your Pooja</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear Devotee,</p>
            
            <p>We're pleased to inform you that <strong><%= panditName %></strong> has accepted your booking for <strong><%= poojaName %></strong>.</p>
            
            <h3>Booking Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> <%= bookingId %></p>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= date %></p>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= time %></p>
            <p><strong>Pandit Contact:</strong> <%= panditContact %></p>
            
            <h3>Your Verification OTP:</h3>
            <div class="otp-box">
                <%= otp %>
            </div>
            <p>Please provide this OTP to the pandit when they arrive to verify the booking.</p>
            
            <p>We wish you a spiritually fulfilling experience.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Vaidic Parampara. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>